text: Paul Raeth (20 November 1898 - 8 July 1989) was a French diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1898 births Category:1989 deaths Category:French male divers Category:Olympic divers of France Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Colmar
